    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a docutils</title>

      <para>
        <application>docutils</application> is a set of
<application>Python</application> modules and programs for processing
plaintext docs into formats such as HTML, XML, or LaTeX.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

